tiers.ability_description: At the end of their turn, Separatist allies gain Defense Penetration Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever an enemy is Stunned, Count Dooku takes a bonus turn.
Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
Whenever a First Order ally defeats an enemy, they take a bonus turn.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
The first time each Light Side ally is defeated, remaining Light Side allies gain 15% Offense and 20 Speed (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.
